---
// ES Yaşam - Hoş Geldiniz Açılış Sayfası
---

<html lang="tr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>ES Yaşam - Daha güzel bir yaşam için</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<style>
			:root {
				--brand-gold: #d4af37;
				--brand-gold-dark: #c5a028;
				--brand-olive: #556b2f;
				--brand-olive-light: #8fbc8f;
				--bg-cream: #FAF8F5;
				--bg-cream-dark: #F5F2EB;
				--text-dark: #2c2520;
				--text-muted: #6e645e;
			}

			* {
				box-sizing: border-box;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}

			body {
				font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
				background: radial-gradient(circle at top, var(--bg-cream) 0%, var(--bg-cream-dark) 100%);
				color: var(--text-dark);
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				overflow-x: hidden;
				position: relative;
			}

			/* Arka Plan Yaprak Süslemeleri */
			body::before, body::after {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				width: 300px;
				height: 300px;
				opacity: 0.08;
				background-image: radial-gradient(var(--brand-olive) 1px, transparent 1px);
				background-size: 24px 24px;
				pointer-events: none;
			}
			body::before { top: 5%; left: 5%; }
			body::after { bottom: 5%; right: 5%; }

			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				width: 90%;
				text-align: center;
				padding: 3rem 2rem;
				border-radius: 24px;
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
				backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
				-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
				border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
				box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(44, 37, 32, 0.05);
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
			}

			.logo-wrapper {
				position: relative;
				display: inline-block;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.logo-ring {
				position: absolute;
				top: -10px;
				left: -10px;
				right: -10px;
				bottom: -10px;
				border: 2px dashed rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
				border-radius: 50%;
				animation: rotate 40s linear infinite;
			}

			.logo-img {
				width: 150px;
				height: 150px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				object-fit: cover;
				border: 3px solid var(--brand-gold);
				box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
			}

			h1 {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--text-dark);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				letter-spacing: -0.5px;
			}

			h1 span {
				color: var(--brand-gold-dark);
			}

			.slogan {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				font-weight: 400;
				font-style: italic;
				color: var(--brand-olive);
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.divider {
				width: 60px;
				height: 3px;
				background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--brand-gold), transparent);
				margin: 1.5rem auto;
			}

			.success-badge {
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				background: rgba(85, 107, 47, 0.1);
				color: var(--brand-olive);
				padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
				border-radius: 50px;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				border: 1px solid rgba(85, 107, 47, 0.15);
			}

			p.desc {
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}

			.btn {
				display: inline-block;
				width: 100%;
				padding: 1rem 2rem;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-gold) 0%, var(--brand-gold-dark) 100%);
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 12px;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1rem;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
				transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
				border: none;
				cursor: pointer;
			}

			.btn:hover {
				transform: translateY(-3px);
				box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
			}

			.btn:active {
				transform: translateY(-1px);
			}

			.footer {
				margin-top: 3rem;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				opacity: 0.8;
			}

			@keyframes fadeIn {
				from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
				to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
			}

			@keyframes rotate {
				100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="logo-wrapper">
				<div class="logo-ring"></div>
				<img src="/images/logo.jpg" alt="ES Yaşam Logo" class="logo-img" />
			</div>

			<div class="success-badge">
				<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
				Astro Projesi Başarıyla Kuruldu
			</div>

			<h1>ES <span>Yaşam</span></h1>
			<p class="slogan">"Daha güzel bir yaşam için"</p>
			
			<div class="divider"></div>

			<p class="desc">
				Leke Çıkartıcı, Sarı Güç ve Mavi Güç lansman ürünlerimiz için hazırlanan ultra-premium, yüksek dönüşümlü e-ticaret satış sayfamıza hoş geldiniz. Ürünlerimizi incelemek, güncel duyuruları takip etmek ve sipariş vermek için bizi sosyal medyada takip edebilirsiniz.
			</p>

			<a href="https://instagram.com/es_yasam" target="_blank" class="btn">
				Bizi Instagram'da Keşfedin: @es_yasam
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="footer">
			© 2026 ES Yaşam & Uçbeyi Gıda. Tüm hakları saklıdır.
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
